Metadata: Ocean and Coastal Law Memo (Issue 34, 35, and 36, July, July, and October 1990)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
Three newsletter issues in one entry for 1990.

The following topics are in these issues: Issue 34: United States Law and Policy Regarding High Seas Driftnets in the North Pacific Ocean, J. A. Ballweber. Issue 35: Recent Developments in Ocean and Coastal Law, 1989 - Oil spill legislation, T. Gross. Issue 36: Developments in Wetlands Law, M. Morris.
